# ===========================================
# Construction Manager - Environment Setup
# ===========================================
#
# This project uses separate .env files for backend and frontend.
# See SECURITY.md for detailed setup instructions.
#
# Quick Setup:
#   1. cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#   2. cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env
#   3. Fill in your API keys (see SECURITY.md for how to obtain each)
#
# Files:
#   - backend/.env   → Server-side secrets (API keys)
#   - frontend/.env  → Client-side configuration (Supabase, backend URL)
#
# NEVER commit .env files to version control!
# ===========================================
